==================
pyLMT Installation
==================

.. contents::
..

Prerequisites
-------------

+ Python 2.7.x

  * http://www.python.org/

  * Only tests with the 2.7.x series

+ setuptools

  * http://pypi.python.org/pypi/setuptools

+ MySQLdb 1.2.3

  * http://sourceforge.net/projects/mysql-python

+ NumPy 1.5.1 or higher

  * http://numpy.scipy.org

+ matplotlib 1.0.1

  * http://matplotlib.sourceforge.net

Building and installing
-----------------------

The setup.py script will invoke easy_install to get any of the
prerequisites that are not already installed, with the exception of
Python itself.

See the site.cfg and LMTConfig.py for details about telling pyLMT how
to find the LMT databases that are available.

  $ tar xvfz LMT-python-0.2.0.tar.gz
  $ cd LMT-python-0.2.0
  $ # edit site.cfg if necessary
  $ python setup.py build
  $ sudo python setup.py install # or su first

